<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SUMMARY</span><br />
D-1221 is objectively a terrible person. Though his past is largely a mystery, we know a few things about him. His last name is 'Schieffer', and he killed his pet cat. Canonically, he dies after the events of SCP-3297 but don't let that stop you from torturing him with anything you want. Knows he's a terrible person and tried fixing it, but he fell back into old habits, ultimately landing in the Foundation as a D-Class. Idenfitifes as male.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DOES HE LIKE HIS COFFEE?</span><br />
He would kill for any form of coffee right about now, to be honest. He hasn't had caffeine in forever.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW OFTEN DOES HE SWEAR</span><br />
Like a sailor.</p>
