<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SUMMARY</span><br />
As a citizen of Wonder World™, Holly has some unusual features. Her eyes are unnaturally large and almost cartoonish, her arms are rubbery, and her eyes change color to reflect her mood. She is the current Dr. Wondertainment in the Wonder World canon and is doing the best she can to improve the company's image following some rather disastrous years of bad leadership. She's very optimistic and always tries to look on the brighter side of things no matter the situation, even though she may not truly believe them to even be remotely possible in the long run. Identifies as female.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DOES SHE LIKE HER COFFEE?</span><br />
She likes her sugar with a dash of coffee. Yes, a dash of coffee.</p>
